2020 Sutherland Sailor Juniors and Seniors,

Reminder that your “Postponed Prom Photo” is due by 8:00pm TONIGHT! Send your Prom Photo to paige.vanskiver@spssailors.org. We want to have some memories to share, so ladies, put on a formal dress and fellas, dress for success and show your school spirit by having your photo taken with Sailor or Sutherland memorabilia! We have gifts for those that show their spirit!

Also, tomorrow night we have prizes to give away! Just LIKE the Sutherland Booster Club page and at 6:00pm we will be hosting LIVE drawings for some amazing prizes! Everyone will end up with a prize or multiple prizes! Encourage your fellow Junior and Senior classmates to attend the LIVE drawing!

We look forward to sharing your photos, giving away prizes, and making 2020 Postponed Prom celebration a memorable one!

This week our high school FBLA chapter hosted a march of dimes money challenge in both high school and elementary.. Friday will be the last day to bring in donations for students! Also on Friday, we encourage all students to wear some kind of purple to show support for babies who were born too early. If you were a premature baby bring in a picture to Mrs. Staggs and that will be posted at our March of Dimes table at the basketball game on Saturday!

Any donations are helpful in helping babies who were born premature.

Have an awesome Thursday!
